column5: I’m truly deeply sorry you had to go through all of that. Your so amazing to say your truth. I hope your have a great life. And I hope this inspires others to get help and know there not alone. Again I’m so sorry.
I’m not saying change but if you live someone you’ll do anything to make them happy cause it makes you feel good. And they’ll do the same for you and love you unconditional
Your doing the right thing. I wish I would have done what your doing. It sucks being with someone who has cheated on you. Wish I would have left day one of knowing.
I’m so truly sorry for your loss. Please take care of your self. Know one day that you can still start a family and life will get better. My heart just aches for you.
Laughed so hard. Made my day
This was so great to read. Live my life the same way and would not change being any other way.
